{% block code_tab %}
    {% filter markdown %}
    ## Installation
    {% include "src/templates/partials/integration.njk" %}
    {% endfilter %}
    
    {% filter markdown%}
    ## CSS block level classes

    | Class name         | Applies to         | Outcome                                             |
    | ------------------ | ------------------ | --------------------------------------------------- |
    | `.eds-page-header-root` | `<header>` element | Defines the outermost container of the Page Header. |

    
    ## CSS Element classes
    
    | Class name                   | Applies to                                                  | Outcome                                                                           |
    | ---------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
    | `.eds-page-header__logo`     | `<div>` element                                             | Defines a container for the Logo                                                  |
    | `.eds-page-header__title`    | Heading level element, such as `<h1>`, `<h2>`, `<h3>`, etc. | Defines a container for the page title                                            |
    | `.eds-page-header__action`   | `<div>` element                                             | Defines a container for the "action" area, typically for a Log in or Log out link |
    | `.eds-page-header__link`     | `<eds-link>` elements.                                      | Modifies link colors to accommodate the brand green background                    |
    | `.eds-page-header__logo-img` | `<svg>` logo element                                        | Formats the Enterprise Logo svg element.                                            |


    ## CSS Modifier classes
    
    | Class name                        | Applies to         | Outcome                                    |
    | --------------------------------- | ------------------ | ------------------------------------------ |
    | `.eds-page-header__legacy-lockup` | `<header>` element | Styles the component with _legacy_ styles. |
        
    {% endfilter %}

    {% set namespace_example_html %}
        <header class="eds3-page-header-root eds-page-header--legacy-lockup">
            <h1 class="eds-page-header__title">My namespaced Header</h1>
            ...
